{"tid":2120950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大17議員聯署 倡懲中港官員","createTime":"2020-07-23T04:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T04:21:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db91a465e2b6120517d8044b9117d0c60ff579a4","tid":2120950,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:20:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200722/4ZXBD6GNKE4CDZ6X7DQY45QTXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2F4ZXBD6GNKE4CDZ6X7DQY45QTXQ%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=82901d7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2F4ZXBD6GNKE4CDZ6X7DQY45QTXQ%2F&h=51b62f40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200722/4ZXBD6GNKE4CDZ6X7DQY45QTXQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n加拿大17議員聯署 倡懲中港官員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xRuD-GdxV7DRkKfoyUHO_W3VY5w=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RJHFLYH6EEULDGSXIGWYDI3QHE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxRuD-GdxV7DRkKfoyUHO_W3VY5w%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRJHFLYH6EEULDGSXIGWYDI3QHE.gif&h=c7842399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜魯多<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】正當英國議員促英國制裁中港官員，加拿大17名跨黨派眾議員向加拿大總理杜魯多發聯署公開信，促請加拿大緊急制裁違反人權之中港官員，並沒收其資產。一直關注香港情況的香港監察創辦人羅哲斯（Benedict Rogers）稱，英、加兩國國會議員選擇在7.21這個特別日子，聯手要求英加兩個政府採取制裁行動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：蓬佩奧訪英 將晤羅冠聰、彭定康<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可沒收違人權者資產<br />\n<br />\n香港監察早前發起行動，促多國政府制裁推動港版國安法及破壞香港高度自治官員，而香港監察昨日發出新聞稿，指繼英國之後，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大國會議員信件指出，中國單方面在港落實港版國安法，違。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港監察董事Johnny Patterson回應加國跨黨派議員要求制裁中港官員公開信時表示。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"bac0eca9546481ca0776246def21933997707742","tid":2120950,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"香槟买什么牌子好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}